title: 400+ Photoshop CS3/CS4 FREE Brushes (for 7.0 and above) Mac / PC
description:
400+ Photoshop CS3/CS4 FREE Brushes (for 7.0 and above)!!



This set contains over 400 Photoshop brushes for use with PS 7.0 and up. These include high resolution brush sets, nature brushes (including waterfalls, clouds, etc.), brushes of abstract twirl designs and circles, moon, stars, trees, smoke brushes, painting stroke brushes, splatter brushes and many more!

To install, extract .zip file

Windows:

Copy/Cut and Paste your brushes to the following folder. You will see your new brushes the next time you open up photoshop.

Program Files > Adobe > Photoshop (whatever version you are using) > Presets > Brushes folder.

Mac:

Copy/Cut and Paste your brushes to the following folder. You will see your new brushes the next time you open up photoshop.

Applications >Photoshop (whatever version you are using) > Presets > Brushes

******** We recommend deleting the contents of your original brushes folder, and replace them with these. This pack already has the built in brushes that came with Photoshop, so there is no need to have duplicates********

PLEASE COMMENT!!!

AND PLEASE PLEASE PLEASE SEED TO A RATIO OF > 0.5!
